        &lt;p&gt;provide a streams-like example for doing word-count maybe?
KStream&amp;lt;String, String&amp;gt; textLines = builder.stream(&amp;ldquo;quickstart-events&amp;rdquo;);&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;KTable&amp;lt;String, Long&amp;gt; wordCounts = textLines
.flatMapValues(line -&amp;gt; Arrays.asList(line.toLowerCase().split(&amp;quot; &amp;ldquo;)))
.groupBy((keyIgnored, word) -&amp;gt; word)
.count();&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;wordCounts.toStream().to(&amp;ldquo;output-topic&amp;rdquo;, Produced.with(Serdes.String(), Serdes.Long()));&lt;/p&gt;

